b:["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"animate-in fade-in duration-500","children":[["$","h1",null,{"children":"Introduction to Kredio"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8 border-l-4 border-cyan-500 pl-4","children":"A credit protocol with memory. Built on Polkadot Asset Hub - live on testnet today."}],["$","h2",null,{"id":"problem","children":"The Problem"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"DeFi lending has not solved credit. It has avoided it. Every protocol built in the last five years operates on the same assumption: trust no one, require overcollateralisation, charge everyone the same rate."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"This works well enough to process volume. It does not work for participants who have built genuine on-chain track records - borrowers who have repaid consistently across months or years, who participate in governance, who carry a verifiable financial history. They get priced identically to a wallet opened this morning."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The data to fix this has always existed. Every repayment, every liquidation, every governance vote is timestamped and immutable on-chain. The obstacle is turning that record into a defensible, manipulation-resistant credit score that materially changes borrowing terms - all inside smart contracts, with no off-chain trust assumption."}],["$","p",null,{"children":"That is what Kredio is."}],["$","h2",null,{"id":"what-it-does","children":"What Kredio Does"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Kredio assigns every borrower a credit score from 0 to 100, computed live at borrow time from four fully on-chain inputs: repayment history, deposit volume, liquidation record, and account age. The score maps directly to a collateral ratio and interest rate - locked into each position at open, with no external oracle and no manual review."}],["$","p",null,{"children":["A first-time borrower at ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"ANON"}]," tier posts 200% collateral and pays 15% APR. The same borrower after twelve repayments reaches ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"DIAMOND"}]," tier - 110% collateral, 4% APR. The improvement is earned entirely through behaviour. No application. No identity verification required. No human in the loop."]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-slate-800/30 border border-cyan-500/20 rounded-lg p-6 my-8","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-cyan-400 mt-0","children":"Live on Polkadot Asset Hub Testnet"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-2 text-sm","children":["All contracts are deployed and active on Paseo testnet (Chain ID"," ",["$","code",null,{"children":"420420417"}],"). Credit scoring, lending markets, PAS collateral market, cross-chain bridge, and the full AI scoring layer are running and emitting on-chain events right now."]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-0 text-sm text-slate-400","children":["Explorer:"," ",["$","a",null,{"href":"https://blockscout-testnet.polkadot.io","children":"blockscout-testnet.polkadot.io"}]," · ","Primary lending contract:"," ",["$","code",null,{"children":"0x1eDaD1271FB9d1296939C6f4Fb762752b041C64E"}]]}]]}],["$","h2",null,{"id":"layers","children":"Three Execution Layers"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Kredio is a hybrid protocol combining three execution environments, each handling what it is architecturally best suited for."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-4 my-6","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-slate-800/20 border border-slate-700 p-5 rounded-lg","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-white mt-0 mb-2","children":"EVM - Capital and Settlement"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-slate-400 mb-0","children":"Solidity contracts on Polkadot Asset Hub EVM handle all capital flows: lending, collateral management, swapping, cross-chain bridging, and XCM intent execution. All user-facing protocol state lives here. Standard ethers.js and viem compatible."}]]}],"$Le","$Lf"]}],"$L10","$L11"]}],null,"$L12"]}]
